data.description: This well kept 2 bedroom 2 bath is available now and move in ready!! 1296 sq ft with bonus room/ den or convert to 3rd bedroom. Freshly painted kitchen cabinets and new flooring throughout home. NEW energy efficient  HVAC to keep you comfortable all year round .  All NEW windows within 2 years.  Living Room features wood burning stove as a second heat source. NEW ceiling fans & garage door opener. Financed Solar at 121/mo completely takes care of the electrical bill.  The HUGE level Back yard has a large covered cement patio and a is completely fenced. Largest portion of fencing is NEW.  Front of the home is also level with 2 car garage, new garage opener and large driveway with boat/RV parking. The small neighborhood of Copper Meadows is conveniently located just off O'Byrnes Ferry Rd near shopping and dining. This home is priced to sell, call today!
